                                    <i class="bi bi-table me-2"></i>@Model.PredictiveGrades9_10.Title (@Model.PredictiveGrades9_10.GradeRange) - @Model.PredictiveGrades9_10.TotalStudents students
                                </span>
                                <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                            </a>
